description:
10/6/2014 from 19:30 to 21:30

Enjoy some wine and be like Pollock...

Join us at Eno Atelier at Rue Dublin 42 at Ixelles, next to Place de Londres.

Book your place!

http://www.eno-atelier.eu/paint-and-wine-event.html


We ALL have wondered if we can paint on canvas. We ALL have wondered if we have a hidden Picasso or Kandinsky inside us. We ALL have wondered if we can change our "normal half", for a couple of hours, with our "creative half"...where ever that is. PaintAndWine is a workshop series that mixes the world of wine with the creative art process. Discover the profiles of known painters, their style and try to create something of your own, under their influence and the influence of wine. Guided by two artists and two different wines, at the intimate space of Eno Atelier, unlock your potential and walk away with a small art piece of your own!
